shortDescription: Enabling gamers to find the perfect teammates
description:
Available in France and in the Nordics, KYKLOS is enabling gamers to find the perfect teammates to enter the amateur esport scene. 
We design a technical and a psychological profile for each user and then automatically push the most relevant profiles to create the best multiplayer experience on the market. Once the team is created, we reward the played time and the performance with a virtual currency which will be spent on our marketplace into discounts on different items.

shortDescription: Molnix Rapid Personnel Manager for humanitarian HR
description: Is your personnel roster still in a spreadsheet? Molnix Rapid Personnel Manager brings proper HR tools to roster management for humanitarian organizations. With it, you can alert the right people in under 60 seconds. By automating and offloading many parts of Human Resource Management, it saves you time and money. We have proven the benefits in operation with the Finnish Red Cross. It is cloud based, available immediately, and works on desktop and mobile. 100% owned by us, but open for angels.

shortDescription: AV-industry, digital signage, construction industry
description:
Seloy Live is providing customized interactive glass surfaces that enable immersive augmented customer experiences.

SENSE - Augmented Interactive Window gives exceptional experiences; Interaction is the key to brand engagement and customer engagement is everything. With Seloy Live SENSE you can make your brand really stand out. SENSE is a state-of-the-art combination of a transparent insulating glass unit and an interactive touch surface, available in any size up to 3 x 6 meters.

shortDescription: Medical devices
description: In many fields of surgery and dentistry, bone has to be cut or removed without damaging the proximal soft structures. Surgify develops new solutions to protect these structures and prevent associated complications. Bleeding, infections and nerve injuries are some of the complications that can severely affect a patients quality of life. Surgify technology improves the safety, speed and precision of bone surgery to minimize these risks.

shortDescription: Textile
description:
IFC's process technology can turn textile, cardboard and agricultural waste to new and better cotton and not only once but infinitely without compromising in quality and comfort. I

FC is running industrial pilot production in Espoo Finland since March 2018 and the material have been successfully proven by major brands and their present supply chain partners. IFC's revenue 2018 is € 1,4 million from fiber deliveries and prelicense product sales.

shortDescription: Viimatech is the cost leader in pump monitoring.
description:
Unique solution to optimize pumps and enable 1 000 000 000 EUR energy and maintenance cost savings in Europe with 30% costs to traditional systems. Extensive, scalable and easy to use solution is based to mathematical methods and cost optimized electronics.
Traction is proven in POC projects in water utilities and process industry. Team combines experience from global tech. business, university science and daily maintenance tasks.
A-round investment 2 MEUR in end 2019 for globalization.

shortDescription: We let you see the quality of water in new light!
description:
Water is set to become the new oil as water scarcity spreads. Understanding the water quality continuously is the key for optimizing the water usage in industry and to prevent pollution.

This can be done with our TWA - Total Water Analyser™ technology, which lets customer truly understand the quality of the water – realtime. 

7 (years University R&D) + 4 (fulltime employees) + 1 (year as startup) = 200 000 (first year revenue)

We are looking 300k€ investment for market segmentation and entry.

shortDescription: Proptech & fintech
description:
We tell property owners, investors and financial institutes where to invest.

Our platform tells you where to put your money to manage both the value and the costs meaning future repairs and maintenance of your real-estate. Both residential and commercial. E.g. if you’re looking at 20000 units in your portfolio and you have a budget to invest in half… which units should you choose and why?

shortDescription: Ohjaa knows what a Chinese traveller wants.
description:
For the first time, a Chinese traveller sitting in his couch at his Xi ´An home can discuss his travel plan `face to face ` with another Chinese standing by a window in his Reykjavik house. For the next 10 minutes, he might decide to talk with someone in Paris. Ohjaa is the first face-2-face trip planning service in the world.

Ohjaa engages 200+ Hosts and the Network covers 17 cities across Europe. We will cover all major European cities with 1000+ Hosts by the end of 2019.

shortDescription: Connecting companies with advisors
description: Boardio connects companies with skilled individuals available for advisory work. Boardio has a global pool of over 2000 candidates with skills and availability for advisory and board positions. Companies needing external advisors can post an recruitment ad for free and let interested advisors apply. Companies can also browse advisor base and contact the ones that seem to have skills needed. Using Boardio is free for both companies and individuals. Premium packages are also available.

shortDescription: Quotation Automation for small businesses.
description:
Small Businesses that sell a complex product, such as manufacturing, or a service, spend a lot of time calculation quotes. 

That's why we have created an easy to use SaaS that allows the business owner to set up a self-service quotation portal for their customers.

We offer the low barrier of entry of something like Shopify, but the flexibility of an otherwise expensive bespoke system.

shortDescription: Aerospace and analytics
description: ICEYE is the first organization in the world to successfully launch synthetic-aperture radar (SAR) satellites with 20-fold weight savings and is the World’s leading company in miniaturized SAR technology. ICEYE empowers others to make better decisions in governmental and commercial industries by providing access to timely and reliable satellite imagery. The company is tackling this crucial lack of actionable information with world-first aerospace capabilities and a New Space approach.

shortDescription: Breakthrough in Electric Energy Storage
description: As global demand for energy continues to grow we need to tackle three main challenges; improving the integration of renewable energies, reducing energy losses and increasing large scale energy storage. Furthermore, we need to oversee the future where we need to be 100% powered by renewable assets, we need to have our grid security designed to withstand heavy drops and loads of renewable energy, also to have a response system to react to rapid load demand from consumers and industries.

shortDescription: Software-based solutions for ecological driving
description:
Our solutions eGRIP and eDAS aggregate data from vehicles and third-party sources to cloud where it is analyzed as real-time slipperiness, vehicle, driving style and traffic flow optimization information. The refined data is then sold to various third-party sources as insurance companies and logistics companies. 
The solution is scalable (SaaS) service for transporters, public transportation, logistics and road maintenance operators. We are looking for funding for geographical expansion.

shortDescription: World's smartest travel diary & sharing platform
description:
Wowanders automatically turns your trips into diaries and makes it easy to share recommendations on hotels, restaurants & sights with friends. By automating content creation we fundamentally change how people can share experiences.
Our revenues come from booking commissions and we're aiming at 45M€ revenues  in 2021.
In few months after soft-launching we already had 5 000 downloads and users had added 2500 trips.
We have gathered so far 200K€ financing, and next step is 500-800K€ seed round.

shortDescription: IoT, Smart Home, Smart Living
description:
Cozify makes smart devices play together. Cozify connects smart devices from different manufacturers into one seamlessly working entity. It provides a single application to control and automate homes and buildings – taking care of security, energy saving and comfort.

Cozify is already a popular end-user product and we have traction in partner sales. Our main goal is to offer a platform for other enterprises to make their own smart living offering.

shortDescription: #1 Catering
#1 Catering
Wellbeing and telehealthcare
description:
Rapidly growing cost of elderly care becomes unbearable unless independent living at home can be extended.
Our solution consists of the Navigil S1/S3 mobile telehealthcare wristwatches with mobile phone, GPS tracking and activity monitoring features supported by mobile communication, location and Navigil Rafael management services which enable blended care model and optimal use of scarce care resources. Up to 30% of healthcare cost can be avoided with preventive care of elderly persons.

shortDescription: Turn health data into valuable information
description:
Spe3dLab is an open source data analysis platform to turn health data into valuable information. The tool was co-developed and co-designed with INSERM laboratories in France, as well as practicians at AP-HP and CHRU Brest.
Spe3dLab is involved in various proof of concept projects in the following fields: reanimation, hospital hygiene, ambulatory as well as forensic medicine units and in a mutual insurance project.

shortDescription: Robotics, AI, transportation and mobility
description: Best in the class vehicle automation system for difficult environments. The solution is based on intelligent combination of various sensors scanning the surroundings of a vehicle and an artificial intelligence and software developed in-house, which is controlling and navigating the vehicle. It has been tested in harsh Finnish winter conditions. Our automation system is platform free and can convert cars and other vehicles to automated ones so that they can be driven driverless.

shortDescription: Augmented Reality/indoor positioning
description: VimAI provides wide area AR navigation and ubiquitous multi-user AR. The basis of the solution is positioning that is based on image recognition and makes thus location-based AR possible . With VimAI buildings can be converted to augmented spaces filled with virtual things all around. Our key customer segments are process industries, shopping malls and building maintenance companies. Also different public buildings, like museums and opera have been interested in our offering.

shortDescription: Replaces keychains with your mobile phone as a key
description: Lukoton replaces mechanical keys and access tags with the one thing people always have with them: the mobile phone. Access is controlled by Lukoton Key Cloud and existing lock bodies upgraded with easy to install lock adapters. Our target users are professionals that need to carry or pick up and return hundreds of keys to get their job done. Stanley Security has invested in us and we are doing projects together but we are looking for 1-2 MEUR investment to speed up our development and growth.

shortDescription: Fuusio cloud is content publishing platform for 3D
description: Fuusio cloud is content publishing platform for the 3D world. It bridges the gap between the 3D / 360 content you have and the channels of distribution, including web, apps, e-commerce and social media. Everything behind an easy user interface that anyone can use. If you have CAD models, 3D or 360 content and are looking for easy ways to share and deploy, then this one is for you.

shortDescription: The technology of visioassistance without download
description:
ViiBE helps industrial technical support and after sales services operate the best remote diagnosis, reduce experts' displacements, optimize first contact resolution rates and improve technicians and customers' satisfaction through a remote assistance experience.
Our Web application enables experts to see incidents in real time through the back camera of the interlocutor's smartphone, snap and share images or any document, draw on them, guide with augmented reality features and much more.

shortDescription: True. Good. Useful. Make sense of behavior
description:
To make optimal business decisions, one must understand customer needs, wants and desires. Invite your stakeholders to co-create and utilize all other textual feedback. 
Our solution has tools to build and manage an online community, create surveys, maintain discussions, and to present ideas with images, videos, and text. 
You get state-of-the-art analytics, insights, nice visuals and best of the breed natural language processing tools.
An example application is cutting customer churn by 50%.

To make optimal business decisions, one must understand customer needs, wants and desires. Invite your stakeholders to co-create and utilize all other textual feedback. 
Our solution has tools to build and manage an online community, create surveys, maintain discussions, and to present ideas with images, videos, and text. 
You get state-of-the-art analytics, insights, nice visuals and best of the breed natural language processing tools.
An example application is cutting customer churn by 50%.

shortDescription: Fintech
description:
We automate asset trading with AI.

This is how we can adapt to market changes efficiently and accordingly. Managing an automated portfolio of validated strategies helps us to avoid human biases and achieve more sustainable and reliable returns.

We are a team of aspiring financial engineers and statisticians with a courageous mindset. Our vision is to combine the power of algorithms and state of the art statistical innovation with financial markets.

shortDescription: WorkPilots, mobile on-demand job matching platform
description: WorkPilots is a unique mobile-first service that connects young people in need of work with households, companies and organizations which can utilize youth to handle their seasonal, on-demand and sporadic tasks (so-called gigs). WorkPilots approach is building social impact. Organizations can easily find motivated workers at a fair price, young people gain access into the workplace, and at the same time, a positive social impact to combat youth unemployment is created.

shortDescription: Software, Health & Wellness
description: Wellmo is a b2b SaaS company driving the preventive digital health megatrend in insurance business and other selected segments. Our solution is a content agnostic platform enabling branded and differentiated health app leveraging local health content and services. This platform & ecosystem approach is gaining increasing traction on the market. Wellmo has paying customers in 5 European countries and is on a solid growth track at close to 100% p.a. for the third year.

shortDescription: Mobile service, Education
description:
Funzi is an award-winning mobile service from Finland that delivers learning and training to everyone, everywhere.

Funzi’s mission is to provide everyone access to quality learning cost effectively, and to deliver the best learning experience on mobile - with little or no cost to the end-user.

shortDescription: Car as a service digital platform provider
description: Provider of  CaaS digital platform for car dealers and fleet management companies with Saas Business model. Enabling bundling of car financing, parking, fuel, car wash, easy communication with IoT data from cars and integration to ecosystem partners. Car and related service is sold as a one monthly fee. In Finland we are having as our customers and partners big car dealers, Santander, Lähitapiola, Elisa, ABC, Falck. 2019 we aim to expand to  countries in Europe. We seek funding for expansion

shortDescription: AI powered location intelligence software
description: Mapple provides an AI powered location intelligence software to help cities and real estate companies better understand the area they are developing. By applying insights on people, infrastructure and mobility they can evaluate current situation and forecast the impact of their investment. Our team is made of GIS experts, data scientists and growth hackers. We are currently looking for partners, new customers and first seed investment.

shortDescription: MAKE DRINKING WATER WITH  ZERO EMISSIONS
description:
We run on solar, we run off-grid.
We run on solar, no diesel needed.
We run on solar, sunshine doesn't cost a penny.
Make drinking water with zero emissions. Revolutionary SolarRO-system helps you to produce safe and affordable water locally in remote locations. You'll avoid the transport of water and bottled water. Potable water can be made directly from seawater, lakes, rivers, ponds or boreholes.
The products are mobile and scalable to suit your capacity requirements. Powered fully by solar.
